Text: Feeling much better on the next night post vaccine. Took a painkiller for the headache. Drinking more fluids, eating at small intervals and also trying my best to keep moving around. Binge watching really helps too. Hoping that I can get a restful sleep tonight
Name: shivangi

Text: Next afternoon: couldn't sleep well, I was hot & cold all night. In the morning I woke up with a headache so I took a herbal med & went back to sleep. I had to take my SOS anxiety med last night so I could sleep a little. Now I'm fully awake, have slight pain on left side stomach

Text: Note: there were no drives or provision of accessible vaccine for disabled people in my area (East Delhi), and so many disabled and high risk people are still unvaccinated because of this. We also need spaces where we can ask specific questions about our bodies and illnesses
